<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 20:07:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡要求将腐败审判的证词推迟到战后</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-to-postpone-testimonies-in-corruption-trial-until-after-war/0000018e-0aa7-d5ee-a78e-3ae716790000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的律师向法庭提出动议，要求“只要国家安全局势没有实质性变化”就推迟作证，理由是加沙战争导致总理与其法律团队之间沟通困难。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:44:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-to-postpone-testimonies-in-corruption-trial-until-after-war/0000018e-0aa7-d5ee-a78e-3ae716790000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家委员会关于梅龙山灾难的报告将于本周发布</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-report-on-mount-meron-disaster-to-be-released-this-week/0000018e-0ac9-d857-adff-cff946cf0000</link><description>2021 年 4 月，以色列北部梅龙山的 Lag B&amp;#39;Omer 庆祝活动期间发生人群拥挤事件，造成 45 人死亡。调查委员会询问了包括总理内塔尼亚胡和警察局长在内的证人，并警告说“他们可能会受到该报告的影响”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:39:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-report-on-mount-meron-disaster-to-be-released-this-week/0000018e-0ac9-d857-adff-cff946cf0000</guid></item><item><title>抵达以色列机场的乘客报告称，由于司机对新的 Gett 政策做出反应，出租车等待时间为两小时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/passengers-arriving-in-israel-report-two-hour-wait-for-cabs-as-gett-changes-pick-up-policy/0000018e-0a7e-d5ee-a78e-3afebb2b0000</link><description>Gett 是一家实际上垄断了以色列出租车市场的叫车公司，它改变了在本古里安机场的接机政策，要求乘客通过他们的应用程序或在信息亭订购出租车，而不是使用现金</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:24:04 GMT</pubDate><gui